castAddBody.text: Hello Farcaster. This is my first cast. Very excited. Coming to you live from Singapore, as it is Singapore FinTech Festival. If you’re at #SFF say hi

Not sure a Suggested User List (SUL) is best for onboarding. I presume Twitter still has this, but I think Dave Winer did a pretty good job writing against it a while back (no secret, I’m in his camp)
Seen right outside Singapore Fintech Festival https://i.imgur.com/gcOwtiL.jpg
Who remembers Peepeth?

“It's easier to start Bitcoin than to reform the Fed. It's easier to start a new country than it is to reform the FDA.” —   on reform, since if a company does something wrong you cancel the subscription; you tend to fight regulators #SFF2022

You want the rest of the world to onboard to web3? They better not have a tough onboard.
